(226, 40, 'cf_anchor1_eng', '<p>Để yêu cầu cung cấp một dịch vụ giám định, trước hết khách hàng có thể liên hệ để có những thông tin ban đầu cần thiết qua</p>\r\n<table class=\"tblGuide\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">Add</span></th>\r\n<td>4/6 no.3 St., Ward Binh An, 2 Dist, HCMC, Viet Nam</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">HO Tel</span></th>\r\n<td>08.22531519 – 08.22531517</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">HO Fax</span></th>\r\n<td>08.62960188</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">Email</span></th>\r\n<td>nvco@hcm.vnn.vn</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">Website</span></th>\r\n<td>www.navicontrol.com.vn</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">Director</span></th>\r\n<td>0903.918.170<span class=\"pc\"><strong>Email</strong>longnvc@navicontrol.com.vn</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th><span class=\"style\">Deputy Director</span></th>\r\n<td>0909.105.666<span class=\"pc\"><strong>Email</strong>dcmtri@navicontrol.com.vn</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>For small and separated services, after getting agreement of client on the survey fee, or any information appointing us, our surveyor come without delay to place and receive official application before carrying out the inspection. Please refer to the “Application form” on this website. </p>\r\n<p>Services with survey fee to be discussed several times, if agreement finally got, the two parties proceed from a signature of an inspection agreement including Inernet contracting, with stipulated items as per Vietnam economic contracting laws. In any way, the official agreement will be etablished thereof in 2 copies (one for each side). Please refer to the form “Inspection agreement” on this website. </p>\r\n<p>Survey report issueing time will meet to satisfy the client requirement indicated on inspection application/agreement forms after receiving their comment to our draft through fax or email way. Finally, the official survey report as well as attached invoice will be delivered to the client hand by our staff members or by express mailling.</p>'),
