(3213, 114, 'cf_content_eng', '<p>This service is the general one and usually ordered by the owners/agents, carriers, insurers, businessmen… Therefor marine survey often held on board the ships or at port area.</p>\r\n<p>Apart from measurement, quality, condition/damage inspection services as above-mentioned, our marine survey division could supply following particular services:</p>\r\n<p>          -  Draft survey</p>\r\n<p>          -  Onhire/offhire/ (partly or fully) of vessel</p>\r\n<p>          -  Onhire/offhire/ interchange survey of container</p>\r\n<p>          -  Pre-loading cargoworthiness survey of mean of transportation/container on cleanliness, tightness, engine/equipment, temperature …</p>\r\n<p>          -  Supervision of loading/discharge of object to or from mean/container on quantity (if tallying required), condition of packing, progress rate of work, temperature of mean/container, temperature of object loaded/to be loaded.</p>\r\n<p>          -  Stowage factor of ship’s hold/of cargo loaded/to be loaded calculation service</p>\r\n<p>          -  Volume measurement of ship’s hold/container for freightingpurpose</p>\r\n<p>          -  Cargo plan preparation service</p>\r\n<p>          -  Bunker survey</p>\r\n<p>          -  Lashing Survey</p>\r\n<p>          -  Pre/post repaire inspection of ship/container</p>\r\n<p>          -  Sucuring/towing survey</p>\r\n<p>          -  Detecting toxic gas leaking service</p>\r\n<p>          -  P&amp;I, PTI service</p>\r\n<p>          -  Sealing/unsealing of hold/container service</p>\r\n<p>          -  Consulting/ Supplying general informations to Master</p>\r\n<p>          -  Investigating and following medical treatment of seamen in Vietnam hospital service</p>\r\n<p>          -  And other ones</p>'),
