(3271, 120, 'cf_title_eng', 'Damage survey'),
(3272, 120, '_cf_title_eng', 'field_5b41aa82f5e1b'),
(3273, 120, 'cf_content_eng', '<p>NAVICONTROL surveyors are ready to render service on condition any time and any where with results reported daily and timely to the applicants. When inspection object get damage, extent and cause thereof will be found out and estimated as far acurate as we can. Our surveyors specially give necessary advices to concerned parties to restrict further damage.</p>\r\n<p>          Insurance companies, owners/carriers … are our favorite client of this service as it is a firm guarantee of objectiveness for their customers. In particular, we supply service of estimation of extent of damage caused to building work, workshop, machine/equipment, mean of transportation… by fire, natural calamity or by accident.</p>'),
