(3302, 123, '_cf_title_eng', 'field_5b41aa82f5e1b'),
(3303, 123, 'cf_content_eng', '<h4><strong>1. Real property, building project</strong></h4>\r\n<p>         -  Consulting on design, construction material, building contractor, choice of optima designand building</p>\r\n<p>         -  Strengh of material, of detailled or overall structure inspection</p>\r\n<p>         -  Total investment fund estimation</p>\r\n<p>         -  Construction field supervision</p>\r\n<p>         -  Building work delivery checking</p>\r\n<p>         -  Appraising/evaluation of construction work, of house for the purpose of business, pledge, transferring, asset division</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>2. General cargo</strong></h4>\r\n<p>         -  Tally quantity</p>\r\n<p>         -  Commercial value survey</p>\r\n<p>         -  Damage survey</p>\r\n<p>         -  Stuffing supervise</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>3. Chemicals/ Oil products/ LPG</strong></h4>\r\n<p>         -  Weight survey</p>\r\n<p>         -  Quality survey</p>\r\n<p>Damage survey</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>4. Machinery / equipment – Means</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Since her foundation, NAVICONTROL always get opportunity of serving clients by machine/equipment inspection- one out of our most frequently prefered services.In order to improve this activity, we would like to introduce to Customers more service items of this:</p>\r\n<p>         -  Consulting on purchase, price and installing of machine/equipment</p>\r\n<p>         -  Acting as consignee’s representative to receive machine/equipment from the manufacturer/exporter to receiver delivery places, in responsible of quantity and externalcondition</p>\r\n<p>         -  Securing supervising and certifying, sealing/unsealing, supervision of transport of machine/equipment from arrival port to storing/installing places</p>\r\n<p>         -  Inspection of condition/damage of machine/equipment on transport means and supervising load/discharge process at delivery places</p>\r\n<p>         -  Supervising installing of machine/equipment at fields or at workshop</p>\r\n<p>         -  Inspection of synchronism</p>\r\n<p>         -  Commercial/usable evaluation for business, exchange, transfer, asset liquidation purposes</p>\r\n<p>         -  Inspection for balance of insvestment fund purpose</p>\r\n<p>Appraising</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>5. Baled - packed - bundle cargo </strong></h4>\r\n<p>         -  Supervise/tally quantity/weight</p>\r\n<p>         -  Weighing supervise</p>\r\n<p>         -  Draft survey</p>\r\n<p>Damage survey</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>6. Agricultural products (rice, coffee, grain flour… ) – bulk cargo, fertilize, row materials…</strong></h4>\r\n<p>         -  Supervise/tally quntity/weigh</p>\r\n<p>         -  Quality survey</p>\r\n<p>         -  Draft survey</p>\r\n<p>         -  Means’ condition survey</p>\r\n<p>Damage survey</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>7. Consulting the international standard quality management system ISO 9001:2000</strong></h4>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<h4><strong>8. Consulting survey</strong></h4>'),
